AfroCentric Says Earnings to Jump as Much as 260% in Six Months to Dec. 31

-- B y   A l a s t a i r   R e e d
-- 
2011-03-10T11:00:08Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-10/afrocentric-says-earnings-to-jump-as-much-as-260-in-six-months-to-dec-31.html
AfroCentric Investment Corp. said
earnings per share for the six months to Dec. 31 are expected to
be between 240 percent and 260 percent higher than a year
earlier.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
